						"description": "Logout authenticated user and invalidate current session.\n\n**Authentication:** Bearer token required\n\n**Response:**\n- Success message\n\n**Note:** This invalidates the refresh token associated with current session. Access token remains valid until expiry (15 min) but cannot refresh."
					},
					"response": []
